{"tid":2225227,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人道組織揭發「世衛」駐剛果醫生藉義診之名，性侵當地逾50位女性、致2人懷孕。","createTime":"2020-10-01T06:52:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T15:20:51.000Z","uid":53379,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9739e46be7486f8d9996d30b466cf17769431dca","tid":2225227,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:52:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>人道組織揭發「世衛」駐剛果醫生藉義診之名，性侵當地逾50位女性、致2人懷孕。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n不少國際組織都曾多次爆出「性侵醜聞」，今日（30日）外媒報導，非牟利組織《新人道主義者（The New Humanitarian）》與《湯森路透基金會（Thomson Reuters Foundation）》共同進行了近一年的調查，指在 2018 年至 2020 年 3 月期間，剛果的伊波拉疫情嚴峻，世界衛生組織（WHO）的醫生及職員假藉義診之名，性侵當地逾 50 位女性，其中更有 2 人因而懷孕，世衛回應時承諾調查指控。<br />\n<br />\n剛果爆發嚴峻的伊波拉疫情，造成 2,000 多人死亡，世衛率今年6月宣布在全球範圍內努力遏制疫情蔓延。然而，世界衛生組織醫生卻受到當地婦女提出「性侵」的指控。調查報告指，這些醫生來自世界各地，包括比利時、布基納法索、加拿大、法國、幾內亞科納克里和象牙海岸。這些當地婦女更指控：「許多男人拒絕戴安全套」，至少有2位女性因此而懷孕。<br />\n<br />\n對當地婦女進行性剝削<br />\n訪問提及，一位25歲的清潔女工被邀請到醫生家中討論升職一事，「他關上門告訴我『條件』是現在必須做愛。」清潔女工指：「他開始脫下我的衣服，我往後退一步，但他不停靠向我、脫我的衣服。我開始哭泣，告訴他要停止&hellip;&hellip;但他沒有停下，於是我打開門跑出去。」另一宗案件中，一名32歲的伊波拉康復者指被邀請到一家酒店接受諮詢。在大廳內，她喝了一杯汽水，幾個小時後，她獨自一人躺在酒店房間醒來，認為自己遭到強姦。許多婦女說被迫通過性行為換取工作，更有婦女稱是「就業的通行證」、「男人要求性的習俗已經變得很普遍，這是找到工作的唯一途徑。」<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nSource：BBC<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://medicalinspire.com/web/posts/57700/?fbclid=IwAR3Me69wd1dtr7ObYKvRLeDXb162vl0M8xro8_X5gmX5yuNpzf9KjZVTbdE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedicalinspire.com%2Fweb%2Fposts%2F57700%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Me69wd1dtr7ObYKvRLeDXb162vl0M8xro8_X5gmX5yuNpzf9KjZVTbdE&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=b82e0a2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://medicalinspire.com/web/posts/57700/?fbclid=IwAR3Me69wd1dtr7ObYKvRLeDXb162vl0M8xro8_X5gmX5yuNpzf9KjZVTbdE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-54342356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-54342356&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=6e2e2469\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-54342356&h=71d3178f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-africa-54342356</a>"},{"pid":"1f1a9806a3c203e23a5cb07a533fde2c8ff8a63a","tid":2225227,"uid":346701,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:54:41.000Z","msg":"CHO<br />\n你話佢殺左50個人我都唔覺得佢意外"},{"pid":"6dbe23034ef34c2b670691c306dfc0992cc3ee77","tid":2225227,"uid":82640,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1f1a9806a3c203e23a5cb07a533fde2c8ff8a63a","tid":2225227,"uid":346701,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:54:41.000Z","msg":"CHO<br />\n你話佢殺左50個人我都唔覺得佢意外"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:56:48.000Z","msg":"毫無監管嘅惡勢力<br />\n仲要裝個光環"},{"pid":"7df7612064b9770705b4038c30d87492cadd22dc","tid":2225227,"uid":339272,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">「世衛」</span></span> <br />\n睇下譚德菜就知係仆街黎"},{"pid":"6ce6c1d09cf66009617fff1f3a54e39b03159740","tid":2225227,"uid":363330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:58:45.000Z","msg":"行撚開 痰得菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda66fa1d60a29e9daf7a48c87eb7327de627609","tid":2225227,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T06:59:51.000Z","msg":"醫生食女係佢本事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40eb6c390c441128c8b8079325a4d5aa28540961","tid":2225227,"uid":266569,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"講個笑話：世界衛生組織（WHO）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef9784826218d53cb4c00a15b15784a130f7703","tid":2225227,"uid":66274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"大個先肯承認權力係會令人腐敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class